title BEFORE: public.users Not Derived From athena.users

package "Athena Auth Source" {
  rectangle "athena.users\n193 rows\ncanonical auth identities" as ATHENA_USERS
}

package "App-Facing Schema" {
  rectangle "public.users\n199 rows\nmanual drift + stale records" as PUBLIC_USERS
}

package "Ikiform App" {
  rectangle "auth + business code\nreads/writes public.users" as APP_CODE
}

APP_CODE --> PUBLIC_USERS : runtime reads/writes
ATHENA_USERS -[#111111,dashed]-> PUBLIC_USERS : one-time/manual copy only

note right of PUBLIC_USERS
  Problems:
  - 6 orphan rows not in athena.users
  - no automatic sync on update/delete
  - timestamp/compat columns inconsistent over time
end note
